♪Rain-chilled frost on midnight drear♪

00:11:39.904 --> 00:11:45.569
♪Your honeyed lies still sear my ear♪

00:11:47.008 --> 00:11:52.966
♪I carved your face in memory's sphere♪

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:58.552
♪Yet gained the wounds I'll always bear♪

00:11:59.008 --> 00:12:05.105
♪That drizzled lane where youth stayed♪

00:12:05.408 --> 00:12:11.630
♪Our music drew lovers near♪

00:12:12.512 --> 00:12:18.180
♪At parting pavilion we stared♪

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:19.760
I'm sorry.

00:12:19.860 --> 00:12:24.429
♪Now shadow walks alone in fear♪

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.160
It was my fault.

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:30.040
I'm sorry.

00:12:31.028 --> 00:12:34.080
♪Red candles count night's vigil sheer♪

00:12:34.448 --> 00:12:37.355
♪Breaths stretch through passing years♪

00:12:37.560 --> 00:12:39.160
(I know you still want revenge,)

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:42.600
(but I must take you away.)

00:12:43.764 --> 00:12:46.720
♪Dread waking finds this dream unreal♪

00:12:46.963 --> 00:12:50.649
♪Relentless memory racks with spear♪

00:12:53.939 --> 00:13:00.275
♪Fate begins and ends, I sip the past♪

00:13:00.275 --> 00:13:05.936
♪Love and hatred flow endlessly♪

00:13:06.867 --> 00:13:14.483
♪When spring comes, I see the truth♪

00:13:14.483 --> 00:13:20.582
♪We've changed through the years♪

00:13:20.582 --> 00:13:27.251
♪Cold lamps reflect pear blossom dew♪

00:13:27.251 --> 00:13:34.931
♪Worlds change as streams run west♪

00:13:34.931 --> 00:13:41.957
♪Rains veil hills, gathering sorrows♪

